  <official_title>Open-Label Multicenter Trial of GlivecÂ® (Imatinib Mesylate, Formerly Known as STI571) in Combination With Chemotherapy (MTC) in Patients With Refractory or Relapsed Acute Myeloid Leukemia (AML)</official_title>
