  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to show superiority in complete responses of combination therapy
      MTC plus Glivec in patients with refractory or relapsed AML compared to a historical control
      which was treated with MTC alone.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
